{"tid":1433631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台：機管局稱未來三天限制進入T1離境大堂人士","createTime":"2019-08-08T14:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T14:11:56.000Z","uid":272243,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"820e7036e9b5410507a3d5ecd1a01a4207ca3bea","tid":1433631,"uid":272243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:05:44.000Z","msg":"機管局表示，留意到網上有人發起於明天起、一連三日在機場集會，由明日至星期日、早上6時至晚上11時59分，持有有效機票或於24小時內離港的登機證，以及有效護照的離境旅客，或持有相關証件的機場員工，才可進入一號客運大樓離境大堂的旅客登記行段。<br />\n<br />\n機管局說，有關措施是為維持離境旅客登機過程及客運大樓運作暢順，機場保安人員會在現場協助旅客或機場員工進入該處範圍。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #港台電視31 #機管局 #離境大堂 #T1"},{"pid":"7ff5143eff892200ea8f4b970c088e183b177946","tid":1433631,"uid":272243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:06:17.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"99a333eb00f9f846160e0c56e8ff4b5a6ea6350a","tid":1433631,"uid":272243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:06:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25585fae44c9e8f32c01940d9b05afb360a8a5a5","tid":1433631,"uid":251292,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:07:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講多次<br />\n我地係接機<br />\n係接機大堂到<br />\n唔係離境大堂</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"92dbc6171e336960f01284a3edb0bec801d60fb8","tid":1433631,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:08:14.000Z","msg":"應該驚人派傳單 , 咁只去入境大堂囉"},{"pid":"e2235c23998fc2a0a5a2339b7c98ab5daf8cbb11","tid":1433631,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92dbc6171e336960f01284a3edb0bec801d60fb8","tid":1433631,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:08:14.000Z","msg":"應該驚人派傳單 , 咁只去入境大堂囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:10:11.000Z","msg":"不嬲都話係接機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上之都冇封，今次就咁大陣仗"},{"pid":"388d97c86f0ac7851d2540cc32e9bc4aa5cee228","tid":1433631,"uid":119697,"like":0,"dis